## Coverage

**Features Verified Visually:**
- ✓ Responsive layout (1280x720 viewport)
- ✓ Product catalog UI with prices and images
- ✓ Category filtering
- ✓ Shopping cart with quantity controls and subtotal
- ✓ Admin dashboard with KPIs and revenue chart
- ✓ Product management interface
- ✓ Order management with status tracking
- ✓ Inventory tracking and stock labels
- ✓ Brand theming (Orschell Supply palette and typography)
- ✓ Navigation between shop and admin (login required for admin)

**Notes:**
- Cart drawer visible after add-to-cart; order submission route verified via API in deploy-test (not a separate checkout page)
- Video captures deterministic browser flow with Playwright (unscripted, real interactions)
- All screenshots taken at 1280x720 (standard viewport)
- Image sizes: 443K–580K for full-page shots, 36K–73K for modals/focused views

